{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ce2182eaab","title":"对陈云病况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"37f4cab6fc","index":0,"year":1953,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"ce2182eaab"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"9e4f8e7ee2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中央人民政府卫生部副部长傅连障1953年2月27日关于政务院副总理陈云的病况给毛泽东的报告上。报告说：“陈云的病，入院治疗后量已有了进步，但苏联大夫认为必须比较长期的休养（四至六个月），并建议去苏联疗养较为有益，我亦认为这样好。"},{"id":"b1b78a8d02","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a690765e8b","type":"title","text":"对陈云病况报告的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab"},{"id":"9e4f8e7ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"杨尚昆、刘、周、朱阅，存尚昆处。请尚昆照昨晚所谈，与陈云同志商处，并代我致感问之意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab"},{"id":"b1b78a8d02","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab"},{"id":"12290a8c1b","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab"}],"page":{"id":"45ceb2be11","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ce2182eaab","start":528,"end":528}}}},"__N_SSG":true}